38
00:02:42,030 --> 00:02:43,700
<font color=#FFFF00>Bagaimana ini?</font>

39
00:02:43,700 --> 00:02:46,040
<font color=#FFFF00>Astaga, Hong Si. Hati-hati.</font>

40
00:02:46,040 --> 00:02:47,640
<font color=#FFFF00>Ponselnya kebasahan.</font>

41
00:02:47,640 --> 00:02:49,640
