47
00:03:07,260 --> 00:03:08,660
<font color=#FFFF00>Sebentar, Hong Si.</font>

48
00:03:11,860 --> 00:03:13,730
<font color=#FFFF00>Ayo kita mengeringkan ini.</font>

49
00:03:17,940 --> 00:03:20,440
