00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:29,340
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu masih hidup?</font>

65
00:04:32,610 --> 00:04:33,850
<font color=#FFFF00>Kamu Min Deul Lae?</font>

66
00:04:34,310 --> 00:04:36,820
<font color=#FFFF00>Seharusnya kamu sudah mati. Aku melihatmu di rumah sakit.</font>

67
00:04:36,820 --> 00:04:38,050
<font color=#FFFF00>Tapi bagaimana...</font>

68
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:42,720
<font color=#FFFF00>Siapa kamu?</font>

69
