00:06:49,620 --> 00:06:51,550
<font color=#FFFF00>Ibu akan ke toilet.</font>

115
00:06:54,850 --> 00:06:57,090
<font color=#FFFF00>Kenapa dia tiba-tiba menyuruhku melakukan kencan buta?</font>

116
